snippet.textDisplay:
Probably heard the song about 50 times by now and still discovering new layers to the song.

আধুনিক - ক্লাসিকাল
বাংলার এপার - বাংলার ওপার
মাঝে শুধু একটি দেয়াল
ভালোবাসার টানে দেয়াল পেরিয়ে দুজন শেষে এক সাথে।

Every single thing, starting from their voices, styles, clothes, the decor, the placement of the musical instruments have a message.

Beautiful!

snippet.textDisplay:
I don't get why Coke Studio Bangla is trying to add funky modern music with classical and spiritual songs. They don't 'fuse' entirely. 

They did the same in Dewana. Well, Dewana was worse than this one.
This song was good until 3:20. Arnob's part was completely out of synch with the song.

Thanks To coke studio for leaving Kazi Nazrul's songs from this forced fusion.
